'''欧洲人民党党团'''是[[欧洲议会|欧洲议会]]中的[[右翼|右翼]]政治集团，由[[欧洲人民党|欧洲人民党]]成员政党的议员组成，有时包括独立的[[欧洲议会议员|欧洲议会议员]]和/或来自非附属国家政党的代表。<ref name="Staab2011">{{cite book|author=Andreas Staab|title=The European Union Explained, Second Edition: Institutions, Actors, Global Impact|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=gePMlsVzZI0C&pg=PA67|accessdate=5 August 2013|year=2011|publisher=Indiana University Press|isbn=978-0-253-00164-1|page=67|archive-date=2016-03-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160322041015/https://books.google.com/books?id=gePMlsVzZI0C|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Thomson2011">{{cite book|author=Robert Thomson|title=Resolving Controversy in the European Union: Legislative Decision-Making Before and After Enlargement|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=uRetSyiQubMC&pg=PA103|accessdate=9 August 2013|year=2011|publisher=Cambridge University Press|isbn=978-1-139-50517-8|page=103|archive-date=2019-06-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190605211401/https://books.google.com/books?id=uRetSyiQubMC&pg=PA103|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Ayd?n-Düzgit2012">{{cite book|author=Senem Aydin-Düzgit|title=Constructions of European Identity: Debates and Discourses on Turkey and the EU|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=DTviXmK9zgkC&pg=PA16|year=2012|publisher=Palgrave Macmillan|isbn=978-1-137-28351-1|page=16|access-date=2018-04-11|archive-date=2019-06-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190610005030/https://books.google.com/books?id=DTviXmK9zgkC&pg=PA16|dead-url=no}}</ref>这个党团由[[基督教民主主義|基督教民主]]、[[保守主義|保守]]和[[自由保守主義|自由保守]]倾向的[[政治人物|政治人物]]组成。<ref name="PetersonShackleton2012">{{cite book|author=Tapio Raunio|chapter=Political Interests: the European Parliament's Party Groups|editor1=John Peterson|editor2=Michael Shackleton|title=The Institutions of the European Union|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=oaD01PaTFE0C&pg=PA340|accessdate=7 August 2013|year=2012|publisher=Oxford University Press|isbn=978-0-19-957498-8|page=340|archive-date=2016-05-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160505234447/https://books.google.com/books?id=oaD01PaTFE0C&pg=PA340|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Puig2008">{{cite book|author=Lluís Maria de Puig|title=International Parliaments|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=z2QkONZLFZAC&pg=PA61|accessdate=9 August 2013|year=2008|publisher=Council of Europe|isbn=978-92-871-6450-6|page=61|archive-date=2014-01-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140103080959/http://books.google.com/books?id=z2QkONZLFZAC&pg=PA61|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Thorlakson2013">{{cite book|author=Lori Thorlakson|chapter=Federalism and the European party system|editor=Alexander H. Trechsel|title=Towards a Federal Europe|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=mTndAAAAQBAJ&pg=PT72|year=2013|publisher=Taylor & Francis|isbn=978-1-317-99818-1|page=72|access-date=2020-02-01|archive-date=2020-06-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200614133406/https://books.google.com/books?id=mTndAAAAQBAJ&pg=PT72|dead-url=no}}</ref>

1976年，欧洲人民党作为欧洲政党正式成立。然而欧洲人民党自1953年6月以来就已经存在了，它来自[[欧洲煤钢共同体|欧洲煤钢共同体]]的共同大会，是欧洲最古老的一级政治团体之一。自1999年以来，它一直是欧洲议会中最大的政治团体。

==历史==

[[欧洲煤钢共同体|欧洲煤钢共同体]]（今[[欧洲议会|欧洲议会]]的前身）的共同大会于1952年9月10日<ref name="ENA9892">{{cite web|url=http://www.cvce.eu/obj/composition_of_the_common_assembly_10_13_september_1952-en-5dd0109a-0c6f-47a3-833a-1c482b599a89.html|title=Composition of the Common Assembly (10–13 September 1952)|url-status=live|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140108181442/http://www.cvce.eu/obj/composition_of_the_common_assembly_10_13_september_1952-en-5dd0109a-0c6f-47a3-833a-1c482b599a89.html|archivedate=8 January 2014}}</ref>举行了第一次会议，第一个基督教民主团体在第二天非正式成立，由马安·萨森担任主席。<ref name="EPP-EDChronology02">{{cite web |url=http://www.epp-ed.eu/Group/en/chronology02.asp |title=EPPED Chronology 02 |publisher=Epp-ed.eu |accessdate=17 June 2010 |url-status=live |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090815070808/http://www.eppgroup.eu/group/en/chronology02.asp |archivedate=15 August 2009 }}</ref><ref name="inghistsassen">{{cite web |url=https://translate.google.com/translate?hl=en&sl=nl&u=http://www.inghist.nl/Onderzoek/Projecten/BWN/lemmata/bwn6/sassen&sa=X&oi=translate&resnum=3&ct=result&prev=/search%3Fq%3D1952%2B%2522Maan%2BSassen%2522%26hl%3Den%26sa%3DG%26as_qdr%3Dall |title=Sassen, Emanuel Marie Joseph Anthony (1911–1995) |publisher=Translate.google.co.uk |accessdate=17 June 2010 |archive-date=2001-10-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20011020223533/http://translate.google.com/translate?hl=en |dead-url=no }}</ref>
该集团在78个席位中占有38席，比绝对多数少两席。<ref name="EPP-EDChronology02"/><ref name="EPP-EDIntegration">{{cite web |url=http://www.epp-ed.eu/Activities/docs/chronologie-historique-en.pdf |title=Microsoft Word – 2006EN-3-DEF-CH.doc |format=PDF |accessdate=17 June 2010 |archive-date=2016-03-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303193037/http://www.epp-ed.eu/Activities/docs/chronologie-historique-en.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref>1953年6月16日，共同大会通过了一项决议<ref name="ena4523">[http://www.cvce.eu/obj/common_assembly_resolution_16_june_1953-en-fe53a389-5c07-410f-a190-78e9dcab80d6.html Common Assembly Resolution (16 June 1953) in ''Journal officiel de la CECA'', 21 July 1953, S. 155] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121004170236/http://www.cvce.eu/obj/common_assembly_resolution_16_june_1953-en-fe53a389-5c07-410f-a190-78e9dcab80d6.html |date=4 October 2012 }}</ref>，使正式成立政治团体成为可能。1953年6月23日，正式发表了该团体的《组织法宣言》<ref name="ena9842">{{cite web|url=http://www.cvce.eu/obj/statement_of_formation_of_the_christian_democratic_group_strasbourg_23_june_1953-en-09478896-b282-4020-b454-dbb7253951c3.html|title=Statement of formation of the Christian-Democratic Group (Strasbourg, 23 June 1953)|url-status=live|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140318125226/http://www.cvce.eu/obj/statement_of_formation_of_the_christian_democratic_group_strasbourg_23_june_1953-en-09478896-b282-4020-b454-dbb7253951c3.html|archivedate=18 March 2014}}</ref>，從而正式成立了该团体。<ref name="EPP-EDChronology02"/><ref name="EPP-EDIntegration"/><ref>{{Cite web|last=Welle (www.dw.com)|first=Deutsche|title=Hungary: Viktor Orban's ruling Fidesz party quits European People's Party {{!}} DW {{!}} 18.03.2021|url=https://www.dw.com/en/hungary-viktor-orbans-ruling-fidesz-party-quits-european-peoples-party/a-56919987|access-date=2021-03-18|website=DW.COM|language=en-GB|archive-date=2021-03-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210321035209/https://www.dw.com/en/hungary-viktor-orbans-ruling-fidesz-party-quits-european-peoples-party/a-56919987|dead-url=no}}</ref>

